@ravipesala No, it is not possible in this version now. In next version, we need to change it.
In spark 2.1 and 2.2, spark is using netty 4.0.x, and gRPC is using 4.1.x, and they are not compatible. That is why we can not use gRPC now. But in spark 2.3 spark have upgraded to 4.1.x. So we can use gRPC once we support spark 2.3, then we do not dependent on spark EndPoint framework.
LGTM
